# Blog Platform

A full-stack blog management platform built with Next.js, Express.js, TypeScript, and MongoDB.

## Features

### Authentication
- Register
- Login
- Logout
- JWT Authentication
- Cookie-based Session
- OTP Email Verification
- Password Reset

### User Management
- User Profile
- Avatar Upload
- Role Management
- Permission-based Access Control
- Suspend / Restore User

### Blog Management
- Create Blog
- Update Blog
- Delete Blog
- Blog Categories
- Blog Search & Filtering
- Blog Cover Image Upload
- Blog Gallery Upload

### Admin Dashboard
- User Management
- Role Management
- Category Management
- Blog Moderation

---
### Frontend

- Next.js
- TypeScript
- Tailwind CSS
- Axios
- React Hook Form
- Zod

### Backend

- Express.js
- TypeScript
- MongoDB
- Mongoose
- JWT
- Multer
- Sharp
- Nodemailer

---

## Project Structure

```bash
blog-platform/
├── frontend/
├── backend/
