```

Available environments:

- Local
- Production

---
## Installation

### Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/jojo-valentine/blog-platform.git
cd blog-platform
```

### Backend

```bash
cd backend

npm install

npm run dev
```

### Frontend

```bash
cd frontend

npm install

npm run dev
```

---

## Environment Variables

### Backend

```env
NODE_ENV=development

MONGO_URI_DEV=

JWT_SECRET=

CLIENT_URL=

SMTP_HOST=
SMTP_PORT=
SMTP_USER=
SMTP_PASS=
```

